  Update to new syntax.

  25 Jan 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  thin-1.2.5-r1.ebuild:
  Fix deps, remove spec task when not running tests (to avoid depending on
  rspec unconditionally).

